":"2019-10-07T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"「獨立批判思考 切忌人云亦云」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527d4dc12fa82aa3aad72efe1ed9bd3e71f30b56","tid":1635493,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f40b0e9ccd03d7f0f3739580504b62fc9eab57","tid":1635493,"uid":49170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:54:37.000Z","msg":"睇曬！<br />\n而家唔係收手嘅時候， 而家係修正嘅時候！<br />\n所以黑裝修紅裝飾係正路！<br />\n神獸應只對兩種人<br />\n1.持武/動武者<br />\n2. 黑警"},{"pid":"171de4c72b8fd7d568a4fb2de6592d75d62f88f7","tid":1635493,"uid":322286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:56:11.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"87de7cfc65cac41b3901859d06c2e5250faed7c9","tid":1635493,"uid":4355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"幫推樓主呢篇文既內容<br />\n我同幾個FD都討論過<br />\n但始終有人認為會繼續咁做<br />\n可能比仇恨沖昏左頭腦<br />\n或者我地無佢地睇得咁睇透<br />\n但都想大家明白和勇不分唔係得個講字<br />\n有時要互相接受意見先可以互相補位<br />\n咁先可以走落去<br />\n希望可以勇時勇和時和 收放自如 <br />\n唔知所有和勇對我呢段說話啱唔啱聽都好<br />\n只係想大家諗清楚 我地點先可以嬴<br />\n我唔相信和理非一日可以嬴亦都唔相信勇一日可以嬴<br />\n所以要勇既時候我會勇<br />\n要和既時候我會幫大家KEEP住twitter retweet"},{"pid":"342ff43b059642c5f8f4e0826e8c06d7c794a5c2","tid":1635493,"uid":275467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"神獸又好，裝修又好，最重要係有原因<br />\n之前已經好多手足講左對等原則<br />\n人地出手先/有武器 唔撚駛諗一手一腳一春袋啦<br />\n但係影下相 屌幾句果d 就唔好晒時間喇，出得黎應該自己包好d<br />\n裝修要有目的，唔可以有個中字就做義工，check 清楚定好目標先去做，做完畫隻龜解釋下俾media 知<br />\n同埋各區咁多保皇辦事處，整晒再諗其他啦<br />\n民政處果d 大樓依家要小心，好可能收埋d 狗係入面衝出黎"},{"pid":"ae1a89520c3f5cdda1f47ba2ca80338c7c3f6818","tid":1635493,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:15:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2ce6b082dc191b6717b770a8a13cbbfa6c626a","tid":1635493,"uid":253438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:15:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a72a2f1e7f43006b5818e03f48f64a70a78a27f7","tid":1635493,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1ee98df2234d135e065be77e2f5900a83be0e490","tid":1635493,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aad3acc88b5964f165bf66999fa6dbfb95ad77e","tid":1635493,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:36:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9e5aed272af353ba627f708e39d30a9b277440","tid":1635493,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a51d36def0b36c11cee89f54771d5e97e68dff8","tid":1635493,"uid":157413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:38:12.000Z","msg":"我覺得可以減少暴力情況 但唔係完全停哂 例如神獸真係唔好係唔係都召喚啦 對家真係開拖先 我地先召喚，裝修既話黨鐵，福建佬呢啲一定要keep住，其他真係唔好亂開戰線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:21:33.000Z","msg":"聽落好阻膠 但我地唔可以淪為同敵人同一種人<br />\n唔係咩道德潔癖 我個人好撚冇道德<br />\n而係為大局 未去到嗰一步"},{"pid":"e3b89a8628bfb54cb5e7889a8f1f6f9b5a1b23d5","tid":1635493,"uid":275467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:21:38.000Z","msg":"另外民意真係要keep ga<br />\n成日都話要睇歷史<br />\n有咩人起義係唔睇民意ga?<br />\n我諗有好多勇武手足都講過，好對唔住天琦，五年前我地跟唔上！<br />\n依家民意係一路進化緊，你諗下如果係六月做裝修，你驚唔驚d 民意無晒丫？<br />\n喱段時間文宣組真係好落力，大大個credit 要俾佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係消毒都要時間消化，同埋勇武唔衝果陣其實都可以做下文宣。 tg 有個bot @TwitterHelpBot , 唔該真係每晚得閒入去做retweet, 文宣組連五常法都識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知道無人有心用twitter, 每晚放task 出黎，我地剩係like 同retweet 就得，當我地白痴咁教ga 喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫幫手，每晚十分鐘丫"},{"pid":"426933569626cc765972277353c5e3d8189c664d","tid":1635493,"uid":27993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e5a882b97dea84c3a9d5f21cbcc51076cddf7843","tid":1635493,"uid":2870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"好文必推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTLDR重點 :<br />\nkeep住文宣 民意<br />\n有原則地裝修<br />\n強調抗爭目的<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力 一齊贏<br />\n唔係休息日啊喂！！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:25:31.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其中一個重點係文宣 本地加國際<br />\n本人不善辭令 篇文帶唔出<br />\n我地一定要將我地行為正當化<br />\n帶俾人睇看似盲目破壞暴力中嘅正當性<br />\n<br />\n狗仔都有做依樣野架 只係佢地係錯誤中指鹿為馬 經不起質問"},{"pid":"88a3f56b932e667df983794cb77f2c9f34d44148","tid":1635493,"uid":303887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:25:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f5084d7c7611cea83e828fb0483cad2c2db168b","tid":1635493,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b4148938c176b4bada510f92b9234e47543fb4","tid":1635493,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"592f1ad4a4285378709890aaab707fece9a0d94e","tid":1635493,"uid":198990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dd7f4d768225f711aa0a0ff8f4ee46d6ac6c840","tid":1635493,"uid":27993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdf50a0353630a7ee5c7b5f440237fecc062bd40","tid":1635493,"uid":298354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"「獨立批判思考 切忌人云亦云」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T15:31:57